# GitHub Pages pubblica da docs
site/

# docs/data CSV files are never committed to git — they are deployed directly
# via GitHub Actions Pages artifact (upload-pages-artifact). Committing them
# would hit GitHub's 100 MB per-file limit as the dataset grows, and storing
# them in LFS breaks GitHub Pages serving (Pages only serves LFS pointer files).
docs/data/*.csv
docs/data/manifest.json

!.gitkeep
